import React from 'react';
import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Switch,
  Route,
  Link
} from "react-router-dom";
import {
  Sidenav
} from './components';

export default function App() {
  return ( <
    Router >
    <
    div >
    <
    nav >
    <
    ul >
    <
    li >
    <
    Link to = "/" > Home < /Link> <
    /li> <
    li >
    <
    Link to = "/budget" > Budget Tracker < /Link> <
    /li> <
    li >
    <
    Link to = "/invetory" > Inventory Tracker < /Link> <
    /li> <
    li >
    <
    Link to = "/reports" > Reports < /Link> <
    /li> <
    /ul> <
    /nav> <
    /div> <
    /Router>
  )
}
